dc_title_s: Prospect, Grundris und Gegend der Polnischen vesten Reichs und Handels-Stadt Dantzig und ihrem Werder; edirt von Io. Bapt. Homann, S.C.M.Geog. in Nürnberg.
dc_description_s: Covers Gdańsk and environs. Relief shown by hachures and pictorially. Graphic scale given in Russian and Prussian miles. North oriented to the left. 2 engraved vignettes surrounding view: Prospect der Stadt Danzig. View includes index. 1 map: hand col.; 35 x 57 cm., on sheet 53 x 61 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
